00:19:31.270 --> 00:19:35.270
Just a thing for your trip to that sunny, tropical paradise.

00:19:35.270 --> 00:19:37.270
Very funny, Sam. I'm not going.

00:19:37.270 --> 00:19:39.270
I'll change myself to the bed.

