Sam, I can't do this. I won't do this.

00:20:01.270 --> 00:20:03.270
From this moment on,

00:20:03.270 --> 00:20:13.450
I swear I will have absolutely nothing to do with Mango Island.

00:20:13.450 --> 00:20:15.450
How much longer do I have to do this?

00:20:15.450 --> 00:20:17.450
Till it's soft and tender,

00:20:17.450 --> 00:20:19.450
tree bark is an important staple to the Mangoes.

00:20:19.450 --> 00:20:21.450
They use it for decoration,

00:20:21.450 --> 00:20:23.450
