00:20:23.450 --> 00:20:25.450
They eat bark?

00:20:25.450 --> 00:20:27.450
It's a delicacy.

00:20:27.450 --> 00:20:29.450
So I imagine only on special occasions.

00:20:29.450 --> 00:20:31.450
They rely chiefly on Mangoes.

00:20:31.450 --> 00:20:33.450
How many more of these do I have to peel?

00:20:33.450 --> 00:20:35.450
Well, let's see.

00:20:35.450 --> 00:20:37.450
We have enough for the Mangoes to do

00:20:37.450 --> 00:20:39.450
and the Mango salad niche was

00:20:39.450 --> 00:20:41.450
two more for the Mango pudding should do it.

00:20:41.450 --> 00:20:43.450
Mom, Ferguson and I have been talking.

00:20:43.450 --> 00:20:45.450
You have?

00:20:45.450 --> 00:20:47.450
Are we really going to have to go through with this?

00:20:47.450 --> 00:20:49.450
Why can't dad have a normal midlife crisis?

00:20:49.450 --> 00:20:51.450
A death-defying hobby. Do you want a rock band or something?

