Kids, we need to talk.

00:20:53.450 --> 00:20:55.450
Uh-oh.

00:20:55.450 --> 00:20:57.450
Your father needs to indulge the side of himself right now

00:20:57.450 --> 00:20:59.450
and he's done a lot for the two of you.

00:20:59.450 --> 00:21:01.450
So let's try to give him our support.

00:21:01.450 --> 00:21:04.450
Though I'm always willing to support my family's decisions,

00:21:04.450 --> 00:21:07.450
maybe Mango Island's a bit extreme,

00:21:07.450 --> 00:21:09.450
