00:21:19.450 --> 00:21:21.450
Sooner or later, I'm absolutely positive

00:21:21.450 --> 00:21:23.450
your father will snap out of it.

00:21:23.450 --> 00:21:25.450
Yeah, Mom, you're probably right.

00:21:25.450 --> 00:21:27.450
He'll definitely snap out of it.

00:21:27.450 --> 00:21:33.450
Listen.

00:21:33.450 --> 00:21:39.540
Do you know what that is?

00:21:39.540 --> 00:21:41.540
Well, that's the ancient Mangoes custom

00:21:41.540 --> 00:21:43.540
