Once stripped and repainted,

00:23:47.180 --> 00:23:49.180
Janie can store all her cardigans in it.

00:23:49.180 --> 00:23:51.180
Sorry it's, um,

00:23:51.180 --> 00:23:53.180
coming with us.

00:23:53.180 --> 00:23:55.180
Well, I suppose this will have to do

00:23:55.180 --> 00:23:57.180
