00:23:57.180 --> 00:23:59.180
like our old country house

00:23:59.180 --> 00:24:01.180
in Greenwich.

00:24:01.180 --> 00:24:03.180
Greenwich.

00:24:03.180 --> 00:24:05.180
I weep for Greenwich.

00:24:05.180 --> 00:24:07.180
We may just be forced to build.

00:24:07.180 --> 00:24:09.180
We're dying to find something futuristic,

00:24:09.180 --> 00:24:11.180
yet cozy.

00:24:11.180 --> 00:24:13.180
Imposing yet inviting.

00:24:13.180 --> 00:24:15.180
Like for Guggenheim,

00:24:15.180 --> 00:24:17.180
with fireplaces and bay windows.

00:24:17.180 --> 00:24:19.180
Absolutely.

00:24:19.180 --> 00:24:21.180
You know,

00:24:21.180 --> 00:24:23.180
