00:24:23.180 --> 00:24:25.180
He made a futuristic architect.

00:24:25.180 --> 00:24:27.180
Was an architect's support.

00:24:27.180 --> 00:24:29.180
We're about to embark on an adventure in the South Seas.

00:24:29.180 --> 00:24:31.180
Hey, Dad, you can design them a house.

