01:29:32.950 --> 01:29:34.950
All right, you heard what he said.

01:29:34.950 --> 01:29:36.950
Find Rain, pick a box.

01:29:37.950 --> 01:29:39.950
Hey! Let's see three.

01:29:39.950 --> 01:29:41.950
Hey, it's me, Ferguson.

01:29:41.950 --> 01:29:43.950
And I'm not the one you're looking for, so pick again.

01:29:43.950 --> 01:29:45.950
All right, that's Ferguson.

01:29:45.950 --> 01:29:47.950
Pick another box you're looking for, Rain.

01:29:47.950 --> 01:29:49.950
Come on, Justin.

01:29:49.950 --> 01:29:51.950
Let's see seven.

01:29:51.950 --> 01:29:53.950
It's me, Rain.

01:29:53.950 --> 01:29:57.300
Oh, yeah!

01:29:57.300 --> 01:30:08.320
You win the trip to a bunch of accessories.

01:30:08.320 --> 01:30:10.320
You win the AT&T cordless fun and digital arts machine.

01:30:10.320 --> 01:30:12.320
We'll see you in five, four, seven, on Monday.

